Flicker gets back to his shuttle, lands, and transforms.

Flicker:  Just pick out the stuff you need and I'll get the transport 
ready.

He goes inside, takes a crowbar, and opens a crate with it and begins 
to get out wheels.  Nearby is any almost inperceptible secret 
compartment, but he throws the lid of the box over it just in case.
